channel.title: MODEL WORK
channel.description: Is there any one who models for HL who could take a model of the Hgrunt that I have get rid of his first aid bag and replace the assault rifle with a model of the MP5 that I have? It would much appreciated. It will only be used for my own personal use and will not be in any mods or anything like that. If you are willing to do this for me please email me at [email]us11bravoang@aol.com[/email] with the subject as "MODEL WORK" for the models. Thanks in advance.
